        "r2": {
          "type": "review",
          "settings": {
            "quote": "Phew that was fast! If you are looking for a quick in between pilates and going to pick up your kids \u2014 THIS IS THE PLACE! Grace was so kind! Also it's very affordable compared to what is out there.",
