            "location": "Houston, TX"
          }
        },
        "r4": {
          "type": "review",
          "settings": {
            "quote": "Abby and Amanda are truly the best! Made me feel so comfortable and they do the best custom tan. I just moved to Houston and had been going to Hush Hush in Dallas and was elated to see there was a Hush Hush right by my house in the Heights.",
